  "texts": [
    "This observation is consistent with our findings that chunk embedding performance improves as the number of chunks retrieved increases from 3 to 5 to 10.",
    "Note that we processed each chunk in separate model calls rather than within a single large context.",
    "Prior research supports the idea that retrieval of most similar document chunks is not always optimal.",
    "For instance, Gan et al.",
    "propose METRAG, which combines a similarity model with a utility model for retrieval, finding that their approach outperforms traditional similaritybased RAG approaches across various QA datasets."
